  <brief_title>Efficacy and Safety of Peginterferon Alfa-2b in HBeAg Positive Chronic Hepatitis B</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase 3, Randomized, Multi-center, Active-controlled, Open-label Study to Evaluate the Efficacy and Safety of Peginterferon Alfa-2b (40kD, Y Shape) in Chinese Chronic Hepatitis B Patients.</official_title>
